`]}),`
`,s.jsx(t.h4,{children:"My experience:"}),`
`,s.jsx(t.p,{children:"I've played this with 7-year-olds and grandparents, and it was really easy to introduce this to them. Nice to have if you want to bring something historical to the table. But not something I'd play every weekend."}),`
